      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Asbury%2C_New_Jersey"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "A Jersey Central Railroad station opened a mile south of Asbury in 1852, yet the village saw little growth after the 1870s.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
