      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Asbury%2C_New_Jersey"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Thomas McElrath, publisher of the New York Tribune, made his summer home in Asbury during the 1870s.",
